they're doing or are they bored? Are they
very good at directing themselves and knowing

00:57:26.240 --> 00:57:27.240
what to do next, or are they just scatterbrained
and you just have to constantly tell them

00:57:27.240 --> 00:57:28.240
what to do?

00:57:28.240 --> 00:57:29.240
And, what you really want is you wanna get
everybody into that sweet spot in the upper

00:57:29.240 --> 00:57:30.240
left corner. How do you get there, right?
Look at each person individually. More water,

00:57:30.240 --> 00:57:31.240
more light, what do they need? If they are
